    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite 6 of 13 credibility factors remaining unassessed and all 7 assessed factors falling below required levels, the assessment team accepts the package at Low assurance level contingent on completion of outstanding epistemic gap analyses prior to regulatory submission. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds hemolysis predictions within a factor of 2.1 of in-vitro measurements, providing sufficient interim confidence for continued development. Full MRL 5 credibility requirements must be satisfied before Class III 510(k) submission.",
